{
  "verses": [
    {
      "verse_num": 1,
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "narrative",
          "text": "The fool says in his heart, 'There is no God.'"
        },
        {
          "type": "speech",
          "text": "There is no God.",
          "speaker": "Fool"
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": [],
      "heading": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": 2,
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "narrative",
          "text": "They are corrupt, their deeds are vile; there is no one who does good."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": [],
      "heading": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": 3,
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "narrative",
          "text": "The Lord looks down from heaven on all mankind to see if there are any who understand, any who seek God."
        },
        {
          "type": "divine",
          "text": "Are there any who understand, any who seek God?",
          "speaker": "God"
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [
        "filthy: Heb. stinking"
      ],
      "references": [],
      "heading": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": 4,
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "narrative",
          "text": "Everyone has turned away, all have become corrupt; there is no one who does good, not even one."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": [],
      "heading": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": 5,
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "narrative",
          "text": "Do all evildoers know nothing?"
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [
        "were…: Heb. they feared a fear"
      ],
      "references": [],
      "heading": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": 6,
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "narrative",
          "text": "They devour my people as though eating bread; they never call on the Lord."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": [],
      "heading": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": 7,
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "narrative",
          "text": "But there they are, overwhelmed with dread, for God is present in the company of the righteous."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [
        "Oh…: Heb. Who will give"
      ],
      "references": [],
      "heading": []
    }
  ]
}